Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.74,0:04:56.04,Planetes - Default,,0,0,0,,{\be1}But Fee-san and the others didn't say anything, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.75,0:04:56.13,Default-jw,,0,0,0,,{\fscx60\fscy60}フィー:phi
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.75,0:04:56.13,Default-jw,,0,0,0,,フィーさんたちは\N何も言わなかったんだろ？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.04,0:04:58.50,Planetes - Default,,0,0,0,,{\be1}You could've denied that you...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.25,0:04:57.67,Default-jw,,0,0,0,,{\fscx60\fscy60}否認[ひにん]:denial/negation/repudiation
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.25,0:04:57.67,Default-jw,,0,0,0,,だったら\N否認という手もあった… あっ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.67,0:04:58.84,Default-jw,,0,0,0,,{\fscx60\fscy60}否認[ひにん]:denial/negation/repudiation
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.67,0:04:58.84,Default-jw,,0,0,0,,だったら\N否認という手もあった… あっ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.95,0:05:02.11,Planetes - Default,,0,0,0,,{\be1}I needed it. I felt like I deserved to be punished.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.96,0:05:02.13,Default-jw,,0,0,0,,{\fscx60\fscy60}罰[ばち]:(divine) punishment/curse/retribution, 罰[ばつ]:punishment/penalty, 罰を受ける[ばつをうける]:to receive punishment/to be punished/to pay a penalty, 気分[きぶん]:feeling/mood
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.96,0:05:02.13,Default-jw,,0,0,0,,（クレア）罰をね\N罰を受けたい気分だったの
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.38,0:05:03.13,Default-jw,,0,0,0,,えっ？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.55,0:05:06.34,Default-jw,,0,0,0,,{\fscx60\fscy60}社会[しゃかい]:society/public|social studies, 一員[いちいん]:person/member
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.55,0:05:06.34,Default-jw,,0,0,0,,（クレア）\N私 社会の一員になりたかった
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.58,0:05:07.77,Planetes - Default,,0,0,0,,{\be1}I wanted to become a member of society.\NTo be recognized as a person.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.47,0:05:08.26,Default-jw,,0,0,0,,{\fscx60\fscy60}認める[したためる]:to write up, 認める[みとめる]:to recognize|to deem|to approve||
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.47,0:05:08.26,Default-jw,,0,0,0,,認められたかった
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.43,0:05:10.93,Default-jw,,0,0,0,,ここにいていいんだって\N思いたかった
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.49,0:05:10.62,Planetes - Default,,0,0,0,,{\be1}I wanted to believe that I deserved to be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.35,0:05:14.23,Default-jw,,0,0,0,,{\fscx60\fscy60}頑張る[がんばる]:to persevere|to insist that|to remain in a place
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.35,0:05:14.23,Default-jw,,0,0,0,,だから テクノーラで頑張ろうって
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.36,0:05:13.86,Planetes - Default,,0,0,0,,{\be1}That's why I worked so hard at Technora.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.39,0:05:15.90,Default-jw,,0,0,0,,ハチには言ったよね？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.40,0:05:18.16,Planetes - Default,,0,0,0,,{\be1}But it's like I said to you, Hachi.\NI couldn't keep up with a thoroughbred.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.02,0:05:18.11,Default-jw,,0,0,0,,{\fscx60\fscy60}サラブレッド:thoroughbred, つきあう:to associate with/to keep company with|to go along with, つきあう:to poke each other/to jab each other, いける:to arrange (flowers)/to plant|living, いける:to be good (at)/to go well|to look (taste, etc.) good
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.02,0:05:18.11,Default-jw,,0,0,0,,サラブレッドとは\Nつきあっていけないって
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.16,0:05:19.10,Planetes - Default,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.23,0:05:19.27,Default-jw,,0,0,0,,（ハチマキ）ああ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.60,0:05:22.11,Planetes - Default,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Maybe I pushed myself too hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.61,0:05:22.19,Default-jw,,0,0,0,,{\fscx60\fscy60}無理[むり]:unreasonable|impossible|forcible||
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.61,0:05:22.19,Default-jw,,0,0,0,,（クレア）私 無理してたのかな
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.11,0:05:25.72,Planetes - Default,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Before I knew it, I couldn't tell what was what anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.32,0:05:25.24,Default-jw,,0,0,0,,{\fscx60\fscy60}気がつく[きがつく]:to notice|to be scrupulous|to recover consciousness
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.32,0:05:25.24,Default-jw,,0,0,0,,気がついたら 何が何だか\N自分でも分からなくなって
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.29,0:05:31.44,Planetes - Default,,0,0,0,,{\be1}When Tanabe-san and I crashed on the moon,\NI thought to myself, "I'm going to die here."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.32,0:05:29.08,Default-jw,,0,0,0,,{\fscx60\fscy60}不時[ふじ]:emergency/unexpectedness, 着せる[きせる]:to put clothes on (someone)|to plate|to accuse (of some crime)
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.32,0:05:29.08,Default-jw,,0,0,0,,タナベさんと\N月に不時着したときにね
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.41,0:05:31.49,Default-jw,,0,0,0,,私は ここで死ぬんだと思った
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.89,0:05:34.60,Planetes - Default,,0,0,0,,{\be1}I thought I would've been better off if I'd been killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.25,0:05:34.21,Default-jw,,0,0,0,,殺されたほうがマシだと思った
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.49,0:05:37.36,Planetes - Default,,0,0,0,,{\be1}But...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.62,0:05:37.58,Default-jw,,0,0,0,,でも…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.34,0:05:48.97,Default-jw,,0,0,0,,{\fscx60\fscy60}結局[けっきょく]:after all|conclusion|ending of a game of Go, 見捨てる[みすてる]:to abandon/to fail/to desert
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.34,0:05:48.97,Default-jw,,0,0,0,,結局 彼女は 私を見捨てなかった
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.36,0:05:48.64,Planetes - Default,,0,0,0,,{\be1}In the end, she didn't abandon me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.12,0:05:52.72,Planetes - Default,,0,0,0,,{\be1}If she had used my oxygen, she could easily have saved herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.30,0:05:53.22,Default-jw,,0,0,0,,{\fscx60\fscy60}酸素[さんそ]:oxygen (O), 確実[かくじつ]:certainty/reliability/soundness, 助かる[たすかる]:to be saved|to escape harm|to be helped
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.30,0:05:53.22,Default-jw,,0,0,0,,私の酸素を使えば\N確実に 助かったはずなのに
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.69,0:06:00.23,Default-jw,,0,0,0,,{\fscx60\fscy60}背負う[せおう, しょう]:to carry on one's back|to be burdened with|to have (something) in the background|
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.69,0:06:00.23,Default-jw,,0,0,0,,私を背負っていた分―
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.71,0:06:03.03,Planetes - Default,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Her O2 usage was higher than mine because she was carrying me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.36,0:06:03.19,Default-jw,,0,0,0,,{\fscx60\fscy60}酸素[さんそ]:oxygen (O), 消費[しょうひ]:consumption/expenditure, 早い[はやい]:fast|early (in the day, etc.)|(too) soon|, みたい:-like/sort of/similar to
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.36,0:06:03.19,Default-jw,,0,0,0,,彼女のほうが\N酸素の消費が早かったみたい
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.24,0:06:07.28,Default-jw,,0,0,0,,{\fscx60\fscy60}いっそ:rather/sooner/preferably
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.24,0:06:07.28,Default-jw,,0,0,0,,いっそのこと―
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.28,0:06:10.12,Planetes - Default,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Right when I was thinking of taking off my helmet and getting it over with,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.41,0:06:10.58,Default-jw,,0,0,0,,{\fscx60\fscy60}ヘルメット:helmet/hard hat/protective headgear, 脱ぐ[ぬぐ]:to take off (clothes, shoes, etc.)/to undress, 楽[らく]:comfort/ease|raku pottery, 考える[かんがえる]:to think about|to ponder|to intend||
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.41,0:06:10.58,Default-jw,,0,0,0,,ヘルメットを脱いで\N楽になろうかと考えたそのとき―
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.29,0:06:13.82,Planetes - Default,,0,0,0,,{\be1}...that's when I saw the shuttle bus.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.29,0:06:13.87,Default-jw,,0,0,0,,{\fscx60\fscy60}シャトルバス:shuttle bus, 見える[みえる]:to be seen|to look|to come, 見える[まみえる]:to have an audience|to face (an enemy)|to serve (esp. as one's wife)
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.29,0:06:13.87,Default-jw,,0,0,0,,シャトルバスが見えたわ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.21,0:06:22.88,Default-jw,,0,0,0,,{\fscx60\fscy60}助け[たすけ]:assistance/help/aid, 求める[もとめる]:to want|to request|to seek|, なんか:things like .../or something like that ... (often derogatory), なんか:something
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.21,0:06:22.88,Default-jw,,0,0,0,,助けを求めるつもりなんかなかった
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.23,0:06:22.57,Planetes - Default,,0,0,0,,{\be1}I wasn't looking to be rescued.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.55,0:06:27.93,Default-jw,,0,0,0,,{\fscx60\fscy60}見捨てる[みすてる]:to abandon/to fail/to desert, ことができる:can (do)/to be able to (do)/can be done
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.55,0:06:27.93,Default-jw,,0,0,0,,でも 私も\N彼女を見捨てることができなかった
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.56,0:06:24.43,Planetes - Default,,0,0,0,,{\be1}But...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.94,0:06:27.65,Planetes - Default,,0,0,0,,{\be1}I couldn't bring myself to abandon her, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.17,0:06:30.46,Planetes - Default,,0,0,0,,{\be1}I wonder why?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.18,0:06:30.80,Default-jw,,0,0,0,,{\fscx60\fscy60}かしら:I wonder, かしら:head|hair (on one's head)
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.18,0:06:30.80,Default-jw,,0,0,0,,どうしてかしらね
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.47,0:06:32.95,Planetes - Default,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Because you liked her?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.51,0:06:32.60,Default-jw,,0,0,0,,{\fscx60\fscy60}好き[すき]:liking/fondness/love, 好き[ずき]:-phil/-phile|being attractive (to)
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.51,0:06:32.60,Default-jw,,0,0,0,,（チェンシン）\N好きだったから？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.01,0:06:36.27,Default-jw,,0,0,0,,{\fscx60\fscy60}まさか:by no means/never!|something unexpected, 大嫌い[だいきらい]:detestable/abhorrent/loathsome
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.01,0:06:36.27,Default-jw,,0,0,0,,フッ… まさか 大嫌いだったわ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.08,0:06:36.66,Planetes - Default,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Not likely. I couldn't stand her.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.66,0:06:39.18,Planetes - Default,,0,0,0,,{\be1}She goes on and on about things she doesn't know anything about...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.85,0:06:39.15,Default-jw,,0,0,0,,{\fscx60\fscy60}言葉[ことば, けとば]:language|word|speech, 振りかざす[ふりかざす]:to raise (esp. overhead)/to brandish (e.g. sword)|to wield (e.g. power, authority)
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.85,0:06:39.15,Default-jw,,0,0,0,,何も知らずに\N言葉だけ振りかざして―
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.18,0:06:41.44,Planetes - Default,,0,0,0,,{\be1}...and thinks that everything can be sorted out if you only try hard enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.27,0:06:41.86,Default-jw,,0,0,0,,{\fscx60\fscy60}頑張る[がんばる]:to persevere|to insist that|to remain in a place
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.27,0:06:41.86,Default-jw,,0,0,0,,頑張るだけで\Nなんとかなると思っている
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.95,0:06:44.72,Planetes - Default,,0,0,0,,{\be1}When I was sent to Debris Section and had to work under her, l...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.98,0:06:44.53,Default-jw,,0,0,0,,{\fscx60\fscy60}デブリ:debris, 課[か]:lesson|section (in an organization)|counter for lessons and chapters (of a book), 回す[まわす]:to turn|to circulate|to surround||
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.98,0:06:44.53,Default-jw,,0,0,0,,デブリ課に回されてね\N彼女の下になったとき…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.65,0:06:46.90,Default-jw,,0,0,0,,{\fscx60\fscy60}怒る[おこる, いかる]:to get angry|to tell someone off|to be angular, 悲しい[かなしい]:sad/sorrowful
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.65,0:06:46.90,Default-jw,,0,0,0,,怒ったり悲しかったりするのは―
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.72,0:06:49.17,Planetes - Default,,0,0,0,,{\be1}When people make you angry or sad,\N it's because you care about what they think.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.03,0:06:49.11,Default-jw,,0,0,0,,{\fscx60\fscy60}気になる[きになる]:to be on one's mind|to feel like|to fancy
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.03,0:06:49.11,Default-jw,,0,0,0,,それだけ\Nその人が気になるからだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.36,0:06:50.24,Default-jw,,0,0,0,,えっ？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.42,0:06:53.72,Planetes - Default,,0,0,0,,{\be1}The opposite of love isn't hate, it's apathy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.45,0:06:53.33,Default-jw,,0,0,0,,{\fscx60\fscy60}愛[あい]:love/affection|attachment, 愛[まな]:beloved/dear, 反対[はんたい]:opposition/resistance|reverse, 憎しみ[にくしみ]:hatred, 無関心[むかんしん]:apathetic/indifferent
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.45,0:06:53.33,Default-jw,,0,0,0,,（チェンシン）\N愛の反対は 憎しみじゃなく無関心
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.72,0:06:56.97,Planetes - Default,,0,0,0,,{\be1}If you didn't care what they thought, you wouldn't hate them.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.83,0:06:56.54,Default-jw,,0,0,0,,{\fscx60\fscy60}相手[あいて]:companion|other party|opponent (sports, etc.), 嫌い[きらい]:dislike|suspicion|distinction, 嫌い[ぎらい]:dislike/hatred/fear
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.83,0:06:56.54,Default-jw,,0,0,0,,どうでもいい相手なら\N嫌いにもならないさ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.20,0:07:00.73,Planetes - Default,,0,0,0,,{\be1}I wouldn't know about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.21,0:07:00.75,Default-jw,,0,0,0,,私には分からない
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.73,0:07:02.65,Planetes - Default,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Oh, I get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.88,0:07:04.34,Default-jw,,0,0,0,,{\fscx60\fscy60}勝手[かって]:one's own convenience|surroundings|convenience||
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.88,0:07:04.34,Default-jw,,0,0,0,,ああ あれだ\N勝手に死ぬなってことだな
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.65,0:07:04.46,Planetes - Default,,0,0,0,,{\be1}I guess it was like you were saying,\N"Don't you dare die on me!"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.46,0:07:07.22,Default-jw,,0,0,0,,{\fscx60\fscy60}論理[ろんり]:logic|logical, つながる:to be tied together/to be connected to|to lead to
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.46,0:07:07.22,Default-jw,,0,0,0,,（クレア）何？ それ\N論理がつながっていないじゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.46,0:07:07.35,Planetes - Default,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Where do you get that from?\N Your reasoning isn't really connected there.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.34,0:07:09.34,Default-jw,,0,0,0,,あっ それそれ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.32,0:07:12.47,Planetes - Default,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Yeah, exactly! A while ago, I had this revelation about what space is.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.47,0:07:12.47,Default-jw,,0,0,0,,{\fscx60\fscy60}こないだ:the other day/lately/recently, 気がする[きがする]:to have a certain mood or feeling/to have a hunch
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.47,0:07:12.47,Default-jw,,0,0,0,,俺さ こないだ\N何か分かった気がしたんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.47,0:07:15.08,Planetes - Default,,0,0,0,,{\be1}I realized that everything in it is connected.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.60,0:07:15.35,Default-jw,,0,0,0,,{\fscx60\fscy60}宇宙[うちゅう]:universe/cosmos/space, つながる:to be tied together/to be connected to|to lead to
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.60,0:07:15.35,Default-jw,,0,0,0,,宇宙ってのは\Nみんな つながってるって
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.56,0:07:16.89,Default-jw,,0,0,0,,{\fscx60\fscy60}つながる:to be tied together/to be connected to|to lead to
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.56,0:07:16.89,Default-jw,,0,0,0,,つながっている？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.58,0:07:16.85,Planetes - Default,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Everything's connected?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.85,0:07:20.00,Planetes - Default,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Somewhere deep down, you and Tanabe are connected, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.06,0:07:19.60,Default-jw,,0,0,0,,{\fscx60\fscy60}つながる:to be tied together/to be connected to|to lead to
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.06,0:07:19.60,Default-jw,,0,0,0,,（ハチマキ）クレアとタナベも\Nどっかで つながってるんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.00,0:07:21.57,Planetes - Default,,0,0,0,,{\be1}It's not just people, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.10,0:07:21.56,Default-jw,,0,0,0,,人間だけじゃない
