Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.47,0:22:50.35,Planetes - Default,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Goodness, what a ruckus...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.47,0:22:50.90,Planetes - Default Alt,,0,0,0,,{\be1}{\an8}Asking the family members of the crew personal questions is prohibited!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.65,0:22:50.82,Default-jw,,0,0,0,,{\fscx60\fscy60}大変[たいへん]:very|immense|serious||
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.65,0:22:50.82,Default-jw,,0,0,0,,（ハルコ）\Nおーおー 大変だこと
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.90,0:22:54.58,Planetes - Default Alt,,0,0,0,,{\be1}{\an8}Anyone who breaks the agreement will have their news permits revoked!
