Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.24,0:22:52.16,Default-jw,,0,0,0,,（九太郎）ただいま
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.30,0:22:52.21,Planetes - Default,,0,0,0,,{\be1}I'm back!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.27,0:22:55.39,Planetes - Default,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Welcome home.\NSounds pretty bad out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.28,0:22:53.41,Default-jw,,0,0,0,,{\fscx60\fscy60}おかえり:return|welcome home
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.28,0:22:53.41,Default-jw,,0,0,0,,（ハルコ）おかえり
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.54,0:22:54.91,Default-jw,,0,0,0,,{\fscx60\fscy60}外[そと, と]:outside|open air|other place, 外[ほか]:other (place, thing, person)|outside|nothing except|, すごい:terrible/dreadful|amazing (e.g. of strength), みたい:-like/sort of/similar to
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.54,0:22:54.91,Default-jw,,0,0,0,,外 すごいみたいね
