Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.12,0:22:56.91,Default-jw,,0,0,0,,（九太郎）取材は\Nお断りって言ってんのに―
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.39,0:22:58.73,Planetes - Default,,0,0,0,,{\be1}We told those guys that we aren't giving any interviews, so what the hell are they thinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.04,0:22:58.29,Default-jw,,0,0,0,,{\fscx60\fscy60}考える[かんがえる]:to think about|to ponder|to intend||
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.04,0:22:58.29,Default-jw,,0,0,0,,何考えてるんだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.73,0:23:01.68,Planetes - Default,,0,0,0,,{\be1}You weren't born yet at the time, so you wouldn't remember,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.79,0:23:00.08,Default-jw,,0,0,0,,{\fscx60\fscy60}生まれる[うまれる]:to be born
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.79,0:23:00.08,Default-jw,,0,0,0,,（ハルコ）\Nあんたは生まれてなかったから―
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.21,0:23:01.71,Default-jw,,0,0,0,,分からないだろうけど―
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.68,0:23:04.31,Planetes - Default,,0,0,0,,{\be1}...but it was exactly the same when your father went to Mars.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.84,0:23:04.38,Default-jw,,0,0,0,,{\fscx60\fscy60}お父さん[おとうさん, おとっさん]:father/dad/papa, 火星[かせい]:Mars (planet)
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.84,0:23:04.38,Default-jw,,0,0,0,,お父さんが火星に行くときも\Nこうだったよ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.50,0:23:05.51,Default-jw,,0,0,0,,（九太郎）へえ
