Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.34,0:23:13.39,Default-jw,,0,0,0,,愛(あい)さん 愛さん 始まってるって
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.72,0:23:15.02,Planetes - Default Alt,,0,0,0,,{\be1}{\an8}I can see Captain Reny and Commander Weher!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.47,0:23:15.25,Planetes - Default,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Sure, just a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.51,0:23:15.02,Default-jw,,0,0,0,,（タナベ）うん ちょっと待って
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.14,0:23:17.14,Default-jw,,0,0,0,,（九太郎）\Nああ もう そんなの俺がやるから
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.25,0:23:17.62,Planetes - Default,,0,0,0,,{\be1}C'mon, I said that I'll take care of that stuff for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.87,0:23:17.62,Planetes - Default Alt,,0,0,0,,{\be1}{\an8}Following them are the chosen elite!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.39,0:23:19.10,Default-jw,,0,0,0,,{\fscx60\fscy60}平気[へいき]:coolness/calmness|all right, くらい:dark/gloomy|dark (in colour), くらい:approximately/about|to (about) the extent that
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.39,0:23:19.10,Default-jw,,0,0,0,,平気だって これくらい
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.62,0:23:19.58,Planetes - Default,,0,0,0,,{\be1}It's okay, I can handle it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.62,0:23:21.39,Planetes - Default Alt,,0,0,0,,{\be1}{\an8}These men and women who will be aboard mankind's first manned mission to Jupiter...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.39,0:23:21.31,Default-jw,,0,0,0,,{\fscx60\fscy60}気にする[きにする]:to mind (negative nuance)/to care about/to worry, すぎる:to pass through/to pass by|to pass (i.e. of time)
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.39,0:23:21.31,Default-jw,,0,0,0,,（ハルコ）\Nそうそう あんた 気にしすぎ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.58,0:23:21.75,Planetes - Default,,0,0,0,,{\be1}She's right, you're worrying too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.39,0:23:23.61,Planetes - Default Alt,,0,0,0,,{\be1}{\an8}...truly have the right stuff!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.44,0:23:22.69,Default-jw,,0,0,0,,{\fscx60\fscy60}うるさい:noisy/loud|annoying
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.44,0:23:22.69,Default-jw,,0,0,0,,（九太郎）ああ うるさい
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.75,0:23:22.57,Planetes - Default,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Who asked you?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.81,0:23:24.27,Default-jw,,0,0,0,,{\fscx60\fscy60}座る[すわる]:to sit|to assume (a position)|to hold steady
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.81,0:23:24.27,Default-jw,,0,0,0,,ほら ここ 座って
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.82,0:23:24.33,Planetes - Default,,0,0,0,,{\be1}C'mon, sit here!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.33,0:23:25.12,Planetes - Default,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Sure, sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.33,0:23:30.63,Planetes - Default Alt,,0,0,0,,{\be1}{\an8}Each small step they take could rightly be said to be a new step in the development of space.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.40,0:23:26.49,Default-jw,,0,0,0,,{\fscx60\fscy60}母[はは, はわ]:mother, 早い[はやい]:fast|early (in the day, etc.)|(too) soon|
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.40,0:23:26.49,Default-jw,,0,0,0,,（タナベ）はいはい\N（九太郎）母ちゃんも早く
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.14,0:23:26.92,Planetes - Default,,0,0,0,,{\be1}You, too, Mom! Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.61,0:23:30.16,Default-jw,,0,0,0,,{\fscx60\fscy60}まったく:really/truly|indeed, いちばん:number one/first|best, 興奮[こうふん]:excitement/stimulation/agitation
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.61,0:23:30.16,Default-jw,,0,0,0,,まったく あんたが\Nいちばん興奮してるんじゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.92,0:23:30.63,Planetes - Default,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Listen to you, you're more worked up than anyone else here.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.63,0:23:32.37,Planetes - Default Alt,,0,0,0,,{\be1}{\an8}And then we turn to the Von Braun,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.78,0:23:32.24,Default-jw,,0,0,0,,{\fscx60\fscy60}実験[じっけん]:experiment, 事故[じこ, ことゆえ]:accident/incident|circumstances
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.78,0:23:32.24,Default-jw,,0,0,0,,（アナウンサー）\N実験中の事故など―
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.37,0:23:33.24,Default-jw,,0,0,0,,{\fscx60\fscy60}不幸[ふこう]:unhappiness/sorrow|death (usu. of a relative), 出来事[できごと, できこと]:incident/affair/happening
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.37,0:23:33.24,Default-jw,,0,0,0,,不幸な出来事もあった―
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.37,0:23:34.66,Planetes - Default Alt,,0,0,0,,{\be1}{\an8}...which has met with her fair share of tragedy while undergoing testing.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.37,0:23:34.70,Default-jw,,0,0,0,,{\fscx60\fscy60}フォン:phon (unit of loudness), ブラウン:brown, 号[ごう]:number|sobriquet|suffix attached to names of ships, trains, airplanes, etc.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.37,0:23:34.70,Default-jw,,0,0,0,,フォン･\Nブラウン号ですが―
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.66,0:23:38.70,Planetes - Default Alt,,0,0,0,,{\be1}{\an8}From this day forward, the name of this ship, the culmination of all mankind's knowledge,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.83,0:23:37.54,Default-jw,,0,0,0,,{\fscx60\fscy60}人類[じんるい]:mankind/humanity, 英知[えいち]:wisdom/intelligence/intellect, 結晶[けっしょう]:crystal/crystallization|fruits (of labor, union, etc.)
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.83,0:23:37.54,Default-jw,,0,0,0,,今日 この日より\N人類の英知の結晶である…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.66,0:23:38.71,Default-jw,,0,0,0,,ああ いた！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.97,0:23:38.69,Planetes - Default,,0,0,0,,{\be1}There he is!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.83,0:23:39.71,Default-jw,,0,0,0,,アハッ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.03,0:23:43.15,Planetes - Default Alt,,0,0,0,,{\be1}{\an8}...will go down in the history books as the ark that carried these great men and women.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.08,0:23:42.67,Default-jw,,0,0,0,,{\fscx60\fscy60}緊張[きんちょう]:tension/mental strain/nervousness
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.08,0:23:42.67,Default-jw,,0,0,0,,八郎太(はちろうた)さん\Nすっごく緊張してる
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.18,0:23:42.37,Planetes - Default,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Look at Hachirota-san, he's so nervous...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.79,0:23:43.71,Default-jw,,0,0,0,,{\fscx60\fscy60}ああん:opening (one's mouth) wide/saying "aah"|crying loudly
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.79,0:23:43.71,Default-jw,,0,0,0,,うん？\N（九太郎）ああん？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.84,0:23:45.63,Default-jw,,0,0,0,,{\fscx60\fscy60}えーっと:let me see/well/errr ...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.84,0:23:45.63,Default-jw,,0,0,0,,（アナウンサー）\Nああっ えーっと…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.61,0:23:46.99,Planetes - Default Alt,,0,0,0,,{\be1}{\an8}Um, what just happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.75,0:23:48.42,Default-jw,,0,0,0,,{\fscx60\fscy60}機関長[きかんちょう]:chief engineer
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.75,0:23:48.42,Default-jw,,0,0,0,,これは何でしょうか？\N星野(ほしの)機関長？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.99,0:23:51.34,Planetes - Default Alt,,0,0,0,,{\be1}{\an8}Chief Engineer Hoshino seems to have done something to his son, Astronaut Hachirota.
