Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.38,0:24:18.00,Planetes - Default,,0,0,0,,{\be1}I know it's a little late, but are you sure you should let him leave like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.56,0:24:17.98,Planetes - Default Alt,,0,0,0,,{\be1}{\an8}...gives us confidence in that this mission will end in success.
